    <title>Hexo on GitHub</title>
    <link href="http://FireCuckoo.com/2017/11/03/Hexo%20on%20GitHub/"/>
    <id>http://FireCuckoo.com/2017/11/03/Hexo on GitHub/</id>
    <published>2017-11-03T14:07:23.000Z</published>
    <updated>2017-11-03T14:57:17.247Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h3 id="Preparation"><a href="#Preparation" class="headerlink" title="Preparation"></a>Preparation</h3><ul><li>GitHub:<ol><li>Register</li><li>New repo: FireCuckoo.github.io</li></ol></li><li>Install Git,Node.js</li><li>Use Git Bash</li></ul><h3 id="Settings-for-GitHub"><a href="#Settings-for-GitHub" class="headerlink" title="Settings for GitHub"></a>Settings for GitHub</h3><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div><div class="line">6</div><div class="line">7</div><div class="line">8</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">cd c:</div><div class="line">cd Users/FireCuckoo</div><div class="line">mkdir MyGit</div><div class="line">cd Mygit</div><div class="line">git init</div><div class="line">git config --global user.name &quot;FireCuckoo&quot;</div><div class="line">git config --global user.email &quot;FireCuckoo@gmail.com&quot;</div><div class="line">ssh-keygen -t rsa -C &quot;FireCuckoo@gmail.com&quot;</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>add C:\Users\FireCuckoo.ssh\id_rsa.pub to GitHub</p><h3 id="Settings-for-hexo"><a href="#Settings-for-hexo" class="headerlink" title="Settings for hexo"></a>Settings for hexo</h3><h4 id="Init-hexo"><a href="#Init-hexo" class="headerlink" title="Init hexo"></a>Init hexo</h4><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div><div class="line">6</div><div class="line">7</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">cd /c/Users/FireCuckoo/</div><div class="line">mkdir hexo</div><div class="line">cd hexo</div><div class="line">npm install hexo-cli -g</div><div class="line">hexo init</div><div class="line">hexo g</div><div class="line">hexo s</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>open URL: <a href="http://localhost:4000" target="_blank" rel="external">http://localhost:4000</a></p><h4 id="Connect-to-GitHub"><a href="#Connect-to-GitHub" class="headerlink" title="Connect to GitHub"></a>Connect to GitHub</h4><p>open <code>~/hexo/_config.yml</code></p><p><code>Ctrl F</code> Search “deploy”</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">deploy:</div><div class="line">  type: git</div><div class="line">  repository: git@github.com:FireCuckoo/FireCuckoo.github.io.git</div><div class="line">  branch: master</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>Git bash:</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">npm install hexo-deployer-git --save</div><div class="line">hexo d</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="Make-it-looks-better"><a href="#Make-it-looks-better" class="headerlink" title="Make it looks better"></a>Make it looks better</h4><p>visit <a href="http://theme-next.iissnan.com/" target="_blank" rel="external">http://theme-next.iissnan.com/</a> to use <code>next</code> theme more features;<br>Use Search Engine, key word “hexo 美化”.</p><h3 id="Connect-GitHub-to-your-domain-name"><a href="#Connect-GitHub-to-your-domain-name" class="headerlink" title="Connect GitHub to your domain name"></a>Connect GitHub to your domain name</h3><h4 id="Local-Settings"><a href="#Local-Settings" class="headerlink" title="Local Settings"></a>Local Settings</h4><h5 id="New-file"><a href="#New-file" class="headerlink" title="New file"></a>New file</h5><p>change directory to  ~/hexo/source</p><p>new a file named <code>CNAME</code>, write in <code>FireCuckoo.com</code>, save.</p><h5 id="Git-Bash"><a href="#Git-Bash" class="headerlink" title="Git Bash"></a>Git Bash</h5><p>open Git Bash<br><code>ping FireCuckoo.github.io</code><br>copy the ip address</p><h4 id="DNS-Settings"><a href="#DNS-Settings" class="headerlink" title="DNS Settings"></a>DNS Settings</h4><p>Go your domain name service:<br>add record<br><code>CNAME WWW FireCuckoo.github.io</code><br><code>A @ 151.101.197.147</code></p><h3 id="First-Post"><a href="#First-Post" class="headerlink" title="First Post"></a>First Post</h3><p>Git Bash:<br><code>hexo new &quot;Hexo on GitHub&quot;</code><br>File Explorer:<br><code>~/hexo/source/_posts</code><br>change the content of <code>&quot;Hexo on GitHub&quot;</code><br>save.<br>Git Bash:<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">hexo clean</div><div class="line">hexo g</div><div class="line">hexo d</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><p>Browser:<br><a href="http://www.FireCuckoo.com" target="_blank" rel="external">http://www.FireCuckoo.com</a></p><p><strong>ALL DONE</strong></p>]]></content>
    
